+// Event codes: STAKE-001 .. STAKE-007
+// Error codes: ERR_STAKE_INSUFFICIENT .. ERR_STAKE_DUPLICATE_APPEAL
+// Invariants:  INV-STAKE-MINIMUM, INV-STAKE-SLASH-DETERMINISTIC,
+//              INV-STAKE-APPEAL-WINDOW, INV-STAKE-AUDIT-COMPLETE,
